headline: Should United Airlines’ IP Flight Tests and NDC Push Require Action From United Airlines Holdings (UAL) Investors?
summary: Boeing recently announced that it worked with United Airlines to flight-test an Internet Protocol-based data communication system on a United 737-8 ecoDemonstrator Explorer, aiming to streamline information flows between cockpits, air traffic control, and operations centers to improve safety, reduce congestion, and cut fuel use and emissions. United Airlines also entered a long-term collaboration with Travelport to co-develop next-generation NDC retailing tools and booking capabilities for...
